snippet.title: Purge Persist and Profit
snippet.description:
Kill alien bugs for corporate gain!
Outfit your employee with the best gear and go spray pesticide across a toxic-yet- mineral-rich alien planet. 
More players means more funding for everyone.
Made for 7DRL 2018
